Vanessa Anne Hudgens (/ ˈhʌdʒəns /; amuru Disemba 14, 1988) bu onye omere na onye ọbụ abụ America

Mgbe o mechara ihe nkiri mpụta mbụ ya na iri na atọ (2003), Hudgens wee bụrụ onye ama ama na-egosi Gabriella Montez na usoro ihe nkiri egwu ụlọ akwụkwọ sekọndrị (2006 – 2008), nke wetara ya nnukwu ihe ịga nke ọma mgbasa ozi.  Ọganihu nke ihe nkiri mbụ ahụ mere ka Hudgens nweta nkwekọrịta ndekọ na Hollywood Records, onye o wepụtara album studio abụọ, V (2006) na Identified (2008).
